item.title: CVE-2024-35232|2024-05-24T20:44:09.233Z -- huandu -- facebook
item.description: github.com/huandu/facebook is a Go package that fully supports the Facebook Graph API with file upload, batch request and marketing API. access_token can be exposed in error message on fail in HTTP request. This issue has been patched in version 2.7.2.
